      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just had a bit of an accident in the kitchen and sliced my forearm pretty good. it's a deep one and just keeps oozing blood even after i press on it for a while. i dont really want to go to the doctor or anything if i dont have to... would it be okay if i just cleaned it out and put some honey on it? i heard that works really well for healing wounds naturally.",
