    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't have the time or the money for a hospital visit right now, and honestly i'm just scared of getting stitches. if i just use a really thick layer of honey and then use some medical tape to hold the edges of the skin together, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as a stitch? i've seen people do this for minor things and it works. can't i just try that first and if it still bleeds tomorrow i'll go in then?",
